Title: Holomorphy, Minimal Homotopy and the 4D, N = 1 Supersymmetric

Bardeen-Gross-Jackiw AnomalyAuthors: S. James Gates, Jr., Marcus T. Grisaru and Silvia Penati

Comments: 16 pp, LaTeX, Replacement includes addition comment on WZNW term and

one new referenceJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B481 (2000) 397-407

By use of a special homotopy operator, we present an explicit, closed-formand simple expression for the left-right Bardeen-Gross-Jackiw anomaliesdescribed as the proper superspace integral of a superfunction.